=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_DiodeRingMod_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark noisy sound, with noise characteristics, featuring instant attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: instant
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 0.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0000
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0000
  pitch_clarity: 0.0981
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -2.8090
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

